'''''Facta''''' is an [[encyclopedia]] in [[Finnish language|Finnish]]. It was published as a series of 11 volumes between 1969 and 1974. It describes subjects from a [[Finland|Finnish]] point of view. Chief editor was [[Veli Valpola]] and publisher, Tietosanakirja Oy.

